Function
========

 PPMuchMore is a text file viewer that allows the user to open multiple
windows and view a unique file in each. To add to the programs flexability
it can also decrunch files packed by PowerPacker ( written by Nico Francois
) and has the option to save the decrunched text to disc.

 When more than one window is open, click in the one you wish to browse.
The windows may be closed in any order.

